name: freq
doc: reference frequency. Set only in Internal reference mode

name: reset
doc: Reset the unit to its default configurations

name: id
doc: Read the SR810 device identification string.

name: local_remote
doc: Set (Query) the Local/Remote state to LOCAL (0); REMOTE (1); or LOCAL LOCKOUT (2).

name: event_status_enable
doc: Set (Query) the Standard Event Status Byte Enable Register to the decimal value i (0-255). *ESE I j sets bit i (0-7) to j (0 or 1). *ESE? decimal value i (0-255). *ESE I queries the byte. *ESE?i queries only bit i.

name: event_status
doc: Query the Standard Event Status Byte. If i is included, only bit i is queried.

name: serial_poll_enable
doc: Set (Query) the Serial Poll Enable Register to the decimal value i (0-255). *SRE I j sets bit i (0-7) to j (0 or 1). *SRE? queries the byte *SRE?i queries only bit i."

name: serial_poll
doc: Query the Serial Poll Status Byte. If i is included, only bit i is queried.

name: power_on_status
doc: Set (Query) the Power On Status Clear bit to Set (1) or Clear (0).

name: error_status_enable
doc: Set (Query) the Error Status Enable Register to the decimal value I (0-255). ERRE i,j sets bit i (0-7) to j (0 or 1). ERRE? queries the byte, ERRE?i queries only bit i.

name: error_status
doc: Query the Error Status Byte. If i is included, only bit i is queried.

name: lia_status_enable
doc: Set (Query) the LIA Status Enable Register to the decimal value i (0-255). LIAE i,j sets bit i (0-7) to j (0 or 1). LIAE? queries the byte, LIAE? i queries only bit i.

name: lia_status
doc: Query the LIA Status Byte. If i is included, only bit i is queried.

name: comm_error
doc: get communication error; for self testing
